{"tid":566668,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊范國威都中伏分享　史泰龍再被誤傳死訊　拍片澄清：死過翻生真係好","createTime":"2018-02-20T06:55:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T07:36:45.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"365b3fd455f9ffa70d77a73203e268ea35dcb8f8","tid":566668,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T06:55:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/punch-05_g6Wxo_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpunch-05_g6Wxo_1200x0.png&h=26b0403a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/28190899_10156285870149924_933711294_n_6qus4_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F28190899_10156285870149924_933711294_n_6qus4_1200x0.jpg&h=b3b41d2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷里活動作巨星史泰龍（Sylvester Stallone）再被誤傳死訊，不少名人信以為真轉發消息。史泰龍本人於社交媒體的官方帳戶澄清，強調自己仍然在生「仲打緊拳」，又拍片笑言「死過翻生真係好」。<br />\n<br />\n繼前年誤傳前列腺癌病逝之後，現年 71 歲的史泰龍近日再誤傳出死訊。是次「死訊」附有史泰龍脫髮照，不少人都信以為真，例如「民主思路」的湯家驊、「新民主同盟」的范國威都先後轉載消息悼念，但很快就因為有網民留言提醒，刪去post。<br />\n<br />\n「死訊」愈鬧愈大，史泰龍本尊當地時間星期一早上於官方帳戶發訊「報平安」。他在 Twitter 呼籲影迷不要理會這些「愚蠢」的消息，強調自己「仍然健在，繼續打拳」。他又在 Instagram 拍片，片中有他和兩名女兒，並寫道「死過翻生真係好」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/personal/湯家驊范國威都中伏分享-史泰龍再被誤傳死訊-拍片澄清-死過翻生真係好/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A%E8%8C%83%E5%9C%8B%E5%A8%81%E9%83%BD%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%8F%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB-%E5%8F%B2%E6%B3%B0%E9%BE%8D%E5%86%8D%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%A4%E5%82%B3%E6%AD%BB%E8%A8%8A-%E6%8B%8D%E7%89%87%E6%BE%84%E6%B8%85-%E6%AD%BB%E9%81%8E%E7%BF%BB%E7%94%9F%E7%9C%9F%E4%BF%82%E5%A5%BD%2F&d=BIV5xndJp99C8eXOj408iFeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=0abb4232\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpersonal%2F%E6%B9%AF%E5%AE%B6%E9%A9%8A%E8%8C%83%E5%9